THE GAME
--------

  'MixTiles' is a Workbench game where the idea is to eliminate
all neighbouring tiles, either horizontally and/or vertically,
that are of the same colour. To complicate matters a lttle, the
tiles are placed in piles of 4 tiles of different colours and only
the uppermost tiles in the piles can be associated with their
neighbours... and the more the number of neighbouring tiles of the
same colour there are, the better it is...

  Avoid isolating tiles, when that happens, the game will still
continue, until there are no remaining neighbouring tiles of the
same colour, but then the game will end...

  Have fun!

